overview: For over 14 years, Nationally Certified Personal Fitness Trainer Mark Darco has helped teach, coach and motivate people to reach their fitness goals in Brooklyn and in NYC. Mark has successfully helped people create beautiful, fit, healthy bodies. With his invaluable knowledge as a personal fitness trainer, he effectively customizes individual exercise programs to meet varied needs ranging from losing weight to improving overall health and sports performance. His clients range from 16 to 75 years in age, including those with particular medical concerns such as asthma and diabetes. Mark is committed to helping people live a more vibrant, healthy life.
